---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="A note to you" description="A personal message from Julius.">
  <div class="text-page">
    <h1>A note to you</h1>

    <p>
      You're reading this because I wanted to share something with you — not just a recipe, but the way I cook.
      The things I make on a Tuesday when I don't know what else to do. The dishes that take twenty minutes
      and somehow feel like an occasion. The ones I've made so many times I've stopped measuring anything.
    </p>

    <p>
      I love cooking for the people I care for. But I can't always be there to cook for you,
      so I built this instead.
    </p>

    <p>
      Every recipe here is something I've actually made - more than once, usually. Some of them are easy,
      some of them require a bit more work, but they are all delicious in their own right and have been
      part of my food rotation over the last couple of years.
    </p>

    <p>
      I hope these recipes bring you as much joy as they brought me. Now get cracking and treat yourself to a nice meal!
    </p>

    <p>
      — Julius
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
